CatDescriptText: The campaign posters on the wall read, "Meet a Winner, Draft Rockefeller". A newspaper, hanging on wall in background reads: Gov. "Rockefeller speaks his mind".  A headline on the copy of the Pittsburgh Courier Rockefeller is holding reads, "Governor Nelson Rockefeller" with a large image of the former governor and vice-president.
TitMainTitle: Four men, two standing reading Pittsburgh Courier, one possibly Nelson A. Rockefeller, possibly in his campaign headquarters
